# V1 _headers smoke for Layero edge.
# V1 path-match scope: `/*` (catch-all) or exact path. No prefix wildcards yet.
# Last write per header name wins, so put `/*` first and override below.

/*
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin

/about/
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex
